{"tid":1334010,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"德國電影精選 German Film Forum: 最後擊戰 A Heavy Heart","createTime":"2019-07-20T03:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T03:20:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2892980651ea73cdb22adff8608ffeebb63d6dbc","tid":1334010,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65695101_2321207307973554_2378946466442903552_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQmBJDbhS02vkWmsWgzgh1k8YOD10kf5HYIlJNywJBjNmw4usOZAL6RjVC46RdVJ_R8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=44d152ab79fc90ae47d61129887d176d&amp;oe=5DE7E5E6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65695101_2321207307973554_2378946466442903552_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQmBJDbhS02vkWmsWgzgh1k8YOD10kf5HYIlJNywJBjNmw4usOZAL6RjVC46RdVJ_R8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D44d152ab79fc90ae47d61129887d176d%26oe%3D5DE7E5E6&h=603a7e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演: 湯馬士﹒史杜柏, 德國, 2015, 109 分鐘<br />\n德語對白，英文字幕 <br />\n<br />\n獎項：<br />\n2018 德國電影大獎－最佳男主角、最佳化妝及傑出劇情片銀獎<br />\n<br />\n荷拔是前東德拳王，但風光不再，如今是夜店保鑣兼收數佬，也算是以拳頭謀生。唯一寄望把徒弟訓練成材，延續擂台上的光輝。他不是好情人，更不是好爸爸，曾經誤入歧途拋妻棄女，落得孑然一身。他不輕易言敗，卻被自己的身體擊倒，以為是普通抽筋，竟被診斷患上「漸凍人症」，肌肉開始萎縮，像霍金一樣逐漸喪失活動及說話能力。迎接人生最後一場「激戰」，意志是力量，而他最想在徹底癱瘓之前，彌補往日過錯，跟女兒重修於好，看外孫女慢慢長大。到底為時已晚，抑或為時未晚？"},{"pid":"30d86f0cedbdd0beb88197d506c745e763f2d9c1","tid":1334010,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2781097465294468/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2781097465294468%2F&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=18942801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2781097465294468/</a>"}]}